item.title: Sanket add a quote by Jim Rohn
item.description: "You are the average of the five people you spend the most time with." -- Jim Rohn

item.title: Sanket add a quote by Pico Iyer
item.description: "We travel, initially, to lose ourselves; and we travel, next to find ourselves. We travel to open our hearts and eyes and learn more about the world than our newspapers will accommodate. We travel to bring what little we can, in our ignorance and knowledge, to those parts of the globe whose riches are differently dispersed. And we travel, in essence, to become young fools again- to slow time down and get taken in, and fall in love once more." -- Pico Iyer
